comments: Bane (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Wiggins' (GSW) path and briefly places two hands on him before disengaging.

Green (GSW) moves along with Clarke (MEM) and establishes himself in a screening position in his path.  Clarke places his hand on Green's back and Green turns with him as the two players briefly engage before the contact dissolves.
Melton (MEM) blocks the shot attempt by Curry (GSW) before it reaches its apex and is on its downward flight towards the basket.
Melton (MEM) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Williams (MEM) places his forearm against Green (GSW) and the contact is marginal as Green attempts to reach for the rebound.
Both Green (GSW) and Wiggins (GSW) jump vertically and the contact with Morant (MEM) is incidental as he releases the pass.
Clarke (MEM) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Green (GSW) dislodges Morant (MEM) from his position during the rebound.
Melton (MEM) reaches in and makes contact with Curry's (GSW) leg during his drive but the contact is marginal.
Morant (MEM) places his hand completely under the ball and brings it to a pause during his drive to the basket.
Thompson (GSW) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
